# ClawUI App: File Browser - APKBUILD
pkgname=clawui-app-filebrowser
pkgver=1.0.0
pkgrel=0
pkgdesc="ClawUI web management for File Browser"
arch="noarch"
license="MIT"
depends="clawui filebrowser"
package() {
    mkdir -p "$pkgdir/usr/share/clawui/apps/clawui-app-filebrowser"
    cp -r "$srcdir"/www/* "$pkgdir/usr/share/clawui/apps/clawui-app-filebrowser/"
    mkdir -p "$pkgdir/usr/share/clawui/apps/clawui-app-filebrowser/api"
    cp "$srcdir"/api/handler.sh "$pkgdir/usr/share/clawui/apps/clawui-app-filebrowser/api/"
    chmod +x "$pkgdir/usr/share/clawui/apps/clawui-app-filebrowser/api/handler.sh"
    cp "$srcdir"/manifest.json "$pkgdir/usr/share/clawui/apps/clawui-app-filebrowser/"
}
sha512sums=""
